Syrul is goddess of lies in the Suel Pantheon of Oerth. She appears as a foul, hideous hag, but in reality she is merely average in appearance. She is the mother of Kord, conceiving him with Phaulkon. Her closest ally is Pyremius.
Her Realm in Khalas is called the Castle of Ugly Truth. Her realm in the Gray Waste is called the Castle of Beautiful Lies. 

